==Finnish==
===Etymology (1)===
===Noun===
'''kato'''

#[[failure]] of [[crop]]s
#[[loss]]

===Etymology (2)===
===Verb form===
'''kato'''
#(''colloquial'') [[look]]!
#:Kato, tuolla on [[neekeri]]! &mdash; ''Look, there's a [[negro]]!''
#(''colloquial'') [[see]]
#:Kato, ei [[neekeri]] ole haukkumasana. &mdash; ''See, [[negro]] is not a pejorative word.''

A corruption of [[katso]], the imperative of [[katsoa]], to [[look]].

===Interjection===
'''kato'''
#(''colloquial'') [[see]].
#:Se on kato sillä lailla. &mdash; ''See, that’s the way it is.''

